window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>On the darkest night, the stars still shine.<br> <br> Feyre’s first Winter Solstice as High Lady is drawing near. With it will come a hard-earned rest from the work that she, Rhysand and their friends have done to rebuild the Night Court and the vastly changed world beyond. Yet the festive atmosphere can’t keep shadows from looming.<br> <br> Even as her own heart heals, she finds that those dearest to her have wounds that go deeper than she knew. And the scars of the past will touch her court in times to come.<br> <br> A sparkling companion tale to the #1 bestselling global phenomenon fantasy series by Sarah J. Maas</p>"; 
